import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import { Form } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import {Backpack, UserCircleGear} from 'phosphor-react';

function NavBar () {

  return (
    <Navbar expand="lg" className="bg-body-tertiary">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand>Voyage-Voyage</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
          <Nav className="me-auto">
             
              <Nav.Link >
                <Link to="/my-account" style={{ 
                  textDecoration: 'none',
                  marginRight: '50px',
                  display: 'flex',
                  alignItems: 'center',
                  color: 'black',

                  }}>
                <UserCircleGear size={32} />
                My Account
                </Link>
              </Nav.Link>
              
            <Form className="d-flex">
                  <Form.Control
                    type="search"
                    placeholder="Search"
                    className="me-2"
                    aria-label="Search"
                  />
                 <Button variant="outline-success">Search</Button>
             </Form>

             <Nav.Link >
                <Link to="/my-trips"
                  style={{ 
                    textDecoration: 'none',
                    marginRight: '50px',
                    display: 'flex',
                    alignItems: 'center',
                    color: 'black',
                    marginLeft: '100px',

                  }}>
                  <Backpack size={32} />
                  My trips
                </Link>
              </Nav.Link>

          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default NavBar;
